text: FK Borac (Serbian Cyrillic: ФК Бopaц Ocтpужницa) is a football club based in Ostružnica, Serbia. ==History== FK Borac was founded in 1931. FK Borac participated in the qualifications for the 2010–11 Serbian Cup. ==References== ==External links== * Club page at FudbalskaZona Category:Football clubs in Serbia Category:Association football clubs established in 1931 Category:1931 establishments in Serbia
